        <h2 class="text-primaryBlue mb-6 text-3xl font-semibold">Our PV Service Process</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="text-primary mr-4 text-2xl font-bold">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-primaryBlue text-xl font-semibold">System Setup & Planning</h3>
              <p class="text-gray">We implement PV databases, PSMF, and SOPs tailored to your regulatory needs.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="text-primary mr-4 text-2xl font-bold">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-primaryBlue text-xl font-semibold">Data Collection & Monitoring</h3>
              <p class="text-gray">
                We handle ICSR processing, literature monitoring, and MICC operations for adverse event data.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="text-primary mr-4 text-2xl font-bold">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-primaryBlue text-xl font-semibold">Analysis & Reporting</h3>
              <p class="text-gray">
                We perform signal detection, prepare aggregate reports, and conduct benefit-risk evaluations.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="text-primary mr-4 text-2xl font-bold">4</div>
            <div>
